ing on. In general, I am a huge fan of the whole 'cute things turn scary' trope, but please understand that this game is so much more than that. I don't mean to compare, but if you're a fan of DDLC, you'll most likely enjoy Siren's Call.\u201d<br>Recommended \u2013 Zee-o<br><br>\u201cThis is, hands down, one of the best visual novel experiences I have ever been through, if not the best. You absolutely will not know what you are about to witness when you play this. Every character feels alive. You will grow to care about every one of them, especially the main character[..]Everything in this game is treated about how it should be in real life, making for a realistic experience that really sits with you.\u201d<br>Recommended \u2013 Casca<br><br>\u201cSiren\u2019s Call: Escape Velocity is a thoughtful coming-of-age story wrapped in a slow-burn mystery that artfully tackles its themes and cleverly takes advantage of the possibilities of the visual novel medium. Come for the thrill and atmosphere and stay for the heart.\u201d<br>9/10 \u2013 Nook Gaming<br>","screenshots":[{"id":0,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469950/ss_8f00d7ebc9deb62338a5a5b9c097abfc2d17165e.1920x1080.jpg?t=1736718511","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469950/ss_8f00d7ebc9deb62338a5a5b9c097abfc2d17165e.600x338.jpg?t=1736718511"},{"id":1,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469950/ss_1c844ad5a7003bd74459f74f887697aaab363f86.1920x1080.jpg?t=1736718511","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469950/ss_1c844ad5a7003bd74459f74f887697aaab363f86.600x338.jpg?t=1736718511"},{"id":2,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469950/ss_4616e36a9ce02a70b56b800edb6ade860a377158.1920x1080.jpg?t=1736718511","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/